Name: BANKACCOUNTNUMBER
Description: Creditor account number. Use 9 or fewer digits, including hyphens and spaces.

Name: ACCOUNTNAME
Description: Creditor account name. Use 16 or fewer alphanumeric characters.

Name: BSBNUMBER
Description: Creditor BSB number, which is the 6-digit hyphenated branch number of the vendor bank account. For example, 123-456.

Name: PYMTREFERENCE
Description: Meaningful reference number to connect the bank file and the bills to be paid, enabling payments to be tracked. Use 18 or fewer alphanumeric characters.
